CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_PARTY_CHILD_SUBTYPE
/* Generated on 20-JAN-15 03.40.06.746566000 PM -06:00 */
AS

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,party_child_subtype_cd IN VARCHAR2
,party_child_subtype_desc IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_child_subtype.add, parms=' || party_child_subtype_cd || '|' || party_child_subtype_desc || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_party_child_subtype a
(
a.party_child_subtype_cd
,a.party_child_subtype_desc
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)

(

,add.party_child_subtype_desc
,'A'

,add.audit_user

,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_child_subtype.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE del (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,party_child_subtype_cd IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2

IS

END da_party_child_subtype;
